    "color": "#00274c",
    "html": "<div class=\"new-canvas\">\n    <section class=\"text-block\">\n        <h2>Overview</h2>\n        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit. Sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit quisque faucibus ex. Adipiscing elit quisque faucibus ex sapien vitae pellentesque.</p>\n        <h3>Objectives</h3>\n        <p>By the end of this module, you will be able to:</p>\n        <ol>\n            <li>Objective 1</li>\n            <li>Objective 2</li>\n            <li>Objective 3</li>\n        </ol>\n        <h3>Focus Your Time</h3>\n        <p>We estimate this module will take <strong>around X hours</strong> to complete. That estimate breaks down into the following efforts:</p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Lecture Videos:</strong> XX minutes</li>\n            <li><strong>Readings:</strong> XX minutes</li>\n            <li><strong>Discussion:</strong> XX minutes</li>\n            <li><strong>Assignments:</strong> XX minutes</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>Module Resources</h3>\n        <p>Please take a moment to download the slides and other resources for this module:</p>\n        <ul>\n            <li>[Hyperlinked Resource Name]</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\">Additional resource information can be found on the <a style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\" title=\"References &amp; Attributions\" href=\"LINK HERE\" data-course-type=\"wikiPages\" data-published=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://courses.online.umich.edu/api/v1/courses/320/pages/references-and-attributions\" data-api-returntype=\"Page\">References &amp; Attributions</a> page.</span></p>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"mo-logo-footer\"><img role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://shared-files.online.umich.edu/michigan-online/course-images/current/michiganOnline.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"318\" height=\"56\" /></section>\n</div>"
